## Commands

### Development
- `npm run dev` — Start development mode
- `npm run build` — Build the project

### Testing
- `npm test` — Run tests
- `npm run test:watch` — Run tests in watch mode
- `npm run test:coverage` — Run tests with coverage

### Code Quality
